{"lemma":"سَبَخاتٌ","slug":"سَبَخاتٌ","root":"س.ب.خ","root_slug":"س-ب-خ","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ب-خ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18686","n18687"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%AE%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sabkha, wet saline plane"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sab.xa/","/sa.ba.xa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18686","headword_ar":"سَبْخَةٌ","root":"sbx","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph, in three places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n18687","headword_ar":"سَبَخَةٌ","root":"sbx","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saboxapN","text_ar":"سَبْخَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract, of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land that exudes water and produces salt:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) pl. (of the former, S, or of the latter, Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sibaAxN","text_ar":"سِبَاخٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, A, Msb, K:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN sabixapN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ سَبِخَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[also] signifies as above; (JK;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land containing"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sibaAx","text_ar":"سِبَاخ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A,) i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"places that exude water and produce salt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or simply]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"salt;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"salt land"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArD saboxapN","text_ar":"ارض سَبْخَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in which the latter word is a contraction of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabixapN","text_ar":"سَبِخَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArD sabaxapN","text_ar":"ارض سَبَخَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also: (Msb:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabixN","text_ar":"سَبِخٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies a place"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"producing salt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and in which the feet sink:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) the pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabixapN","text_ar":"سَبِخَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sabixaAtN","text_ar":"سَبِخَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) The Prophet said to Anas, on his mentioning El-Basrah,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino mararota","text_ar":"اـِنْ مَرَرْتَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihaA wadaxalotahaA faA_iy~aAka wasibaAxahaA","text_ar":"بِهَا وَدَخَلْتَهَا فَاـِيَّاكَ وَسِبَاخَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If thou pass by it and enter it, then beware thou of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its tracts of land overspread with saltness, that seldom,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"never, give growth to anything but some trees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shrubs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b2-  Also, (K,) or the latter, i. e. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saboxapN","text_ar":"سَبْخَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing that overspreads water"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in consequence of its having been long left,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the green substance called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TuHolub","text_ar":"طُحْلُب"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"THlb","text_ar":"طحلب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","A","Msb","TA","JK"]}]}}